        <p id="Par29">For bins that are directly adjacent on the linear genome (namely, |<italic>i</italic> – <italic>j</italic>| = 1, 1 ≤ <italic>i</italic>, <italic>j</italic> ≤ <italic>N</italic>), error vectors are defined as in Eq<italic>.</italic>
